defaultEconomics and Political Science,
default is a 
defaultresearch centre, chaired by Nicholas 
defaultStern
default, which brings together international expertise on economics, finance, geography, international development and political economy.
default Bob Ward is the Policy and Communications Director. Naomi Hicks is the Institute’s Public Communications Manager. 
defaultThe Insti
defaulttute is funded by the Grantham F
defaultoundation for the Protection of the Environment and the Global Green Growth Institute. The work of the Institute is integrated with the activities of the Centre for Climate Change Economics and Policy, which is hosted by the London School of Economics 
defaultand Political Science 
defaultand the University of Leeds, and funded by the UK Economic and Social Research Council and Munich Re.
